summary:

 Beeple Is Our Lord & Saviour, We Need His Help! - We absolutely LOVE BEEPLE & all of his AMAZING Artwork. We have followed his journey & other Artists who are now facing the rise of Ai Generated Images that is destroying this space!

 Our Objective Is To Get Beeple's Attention ASAP! - Once we have Beeple's attention through showing him how much of a POWERFUL COMMUNITY he has behind his Artwork. Then we will be able to move onto the next step of our Beeple adventure!

 Let's Get Beeple's Attention Together! - FYI: He Sold This NFT For $69,000,000 on March 11th 2021
